1
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,120
Why are you here?

2
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,200
Isn't this Jiao Li's phone?

3
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,800
Open it and see for yourself.

4
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,680
Let's go.

5
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,080
Ren Zhen.

6
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,640
Sorry.

7
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,000
Everyone found out you're leaving.

8
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,360
But don't worry,

9
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,240
we've already discussed it.

10
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,660
We won't go see you off.

11
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,600
And we won't hold you back.

12
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,520
Well,

13
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,979
everyone has something to say to you.

14
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,320
Ren Zhen.

15
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:56,120
I just counted,

16
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:58,000
it's been four months.

17
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,120
Time flies.

18
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,640
The first time we met

19
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,320
was in our field.

20
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,120
I was so anxious then

21
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,240
and said some mean things,

22
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,220
but you didn't take them to heart.

23
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,200
You are a good girl.

24
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,440
Later I learned it was Jiao Li

25
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:16,520
who invited you to do live streaming.

26
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:19,360
You are like a fairy from Tianshan Mountain.

27
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,760
Thank you for helping us so much.

28
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,040
Now that you're leaving,

29
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,280
I'll miss you so much.

30
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,680
Don't say that.

31
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,360
It'll make her sad.

32
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,960
Here, let me.

33
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,400
Ren Zhen.

34
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,400
If Wulan hadn't told us,

35
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:40,240
we wouldn't have had the chance to say goodbye.

36
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:43,120
Xia Village is a very small village.

37
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,600
You came to such a remote place.

38
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,120
I am so glad.

39
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,340
Other than that...

40
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,000
I hope to see you again.

41
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:57,520
If you come to Xia Village next time,

42
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,680
I...

43
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,160
I'll make naan for you.

44
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:06,520
Sister Ren Zhen, we don't want you to leave.

45
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,120
My child,

46
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,760
didn't you often say

47
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,440
you love listening to my long songs?

48
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,640
I'll sing a long song for you now.

49
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:28,600
Now I am leaving for a distant land.

50
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:33,760
What kind of place is that distant land?

51
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:41,360
The yurt is lit with dim light.

52
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:47,560
Mother's singing echoes in my dreams.

53
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:51,000
The child holds the lost lamb,

54
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:54,120
looking for the way home.

55
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,480
Renzhen.

56
00:03:59,079 --> 00:03:59,880
Could you

57
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,000
not leave?

58
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,520
Alright.

59
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,380
Why are you being so sentimental?

60
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,490
Hello, Renzhen.

61
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,880
Do you still remember?

62
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:09,960
Do you remember how we were when we first met

63
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,020
at Mr. Yin's house?

64
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,880
At that time,

65
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,280
we had a little mix-up.

66
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,480
It was quite awkward.

67
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,079
I thought back then

68
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,329
that you were a very interesting girl.

69
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,240
Later,

70
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:23,700
you knew we wanted to sell goji berries via livestream.

71
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,960
You went around the village every day,

72
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,320
shooting footage,

73
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,450
coming back to edit videos,

74
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,600
and running the official account.

75
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,400
Keep it up.

76
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:36,800
When you work,

77
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,330
you are just like your name,

78
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,640
very serious.

79
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,400
I was wondering

80
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,040
why you work so hard

81
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,720
and look so happy every day.

82
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,850
It feels like you have endless energy.

83
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,440
Later I realized

84
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,860
that your hard work

85
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,159
and happiness

86
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,740
are actually your strengths.

87
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,880
But it's also

88
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,900
a way for you to protect yourself.

89
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,120
It must be hard for anyone

90
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,920
to see you unhappy.

91
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,600
And no one would notice

92
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:07,100
that you have hurdles you can't get over.

93
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,960
But I saw it.

94
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,920
Jiao Li.

95
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,160
I really miss home.

96
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,370
What did you say?

97
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,680
But I don't have a home anymore.

98
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,680
I don't know where to go.

99
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,860
You don't have to go anywhere.

100
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,880
Like a tree,

101
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:36,280
find a place you like,

102
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,720
put down roots,

103
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,360
and that is home.

104
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,080
Ren Zhen.

105
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,120
Do you like it here?

106
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,280
This place likes you too.

107
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,120
You know what?

108
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,120
Meeting you at Mr. Yin's house,

109
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,120
you have no idea how happy it made me.

110
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,320
Ren Zhen.

111
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,480
I really hope you can stay.

112
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,840
You have your attitude

113
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,760
and ideas.

114
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:09,330
No matter what difficulties you face,

115
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,280
you can always find a solution.

116
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,120
Maybe Xiacun is, to you,

117
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,720
just a brief interlude.

118
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,000
No matter where you go in the future,

119
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,080
I think you definitely have

120
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,800
the courage to start over.

121
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,640
Actually, I really wanted to

122
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,840
freely wish you well.

123
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:27,960
But deep down,

124
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,880
a voice keeps telling me

125
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,340
that I want you to stay.

126
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,400
Since you appeared,

127
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,260
I've been especially motivated.

128
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,520
I know what my goals are,

129
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:43,650
and I work hard towards them every day.

130
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,520
Not just me,

131
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,520
but the whole Xiacun

132
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,440
was given light and energy by you.

133
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,970
But I know I shouldn't be like this.

134
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,760
Because I want you

135
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,520
to be free from any restraints

136
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,960
and be yourself.

137
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,120
Ren Zhen.

138
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:07,140
No matter where you are in the future,

139
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,760
you will always be that

140
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,440
shining star.

141
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,560
Dad Yin.

142
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:25,240
Zhenzhen.

143
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,600
Are you on the bus?

144
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,280
What's wrong?

145
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,920
I feel like I can't leave.

146
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,200
Zhenzhen.

147
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,720
I know.

148
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,800
Since your family left,

149
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,320
you feel that in this world,

150
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:49,280
there's no place you can call home.

151
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,159
But,

152
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,840
a home can be created.

153
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,840
Zhenzhen.

154
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,200
Don't be afraid.

155
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,420
If this place gives you peace of mind,

156
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,240
then here

157
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,680
is your home.

158
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,280
What's the matter? Why the rush?

159
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,880
The county called us to receive an award.

160
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:52,680
Receive an award?

161
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,320
Yes.

162
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,640
Xia Village won the Rural Revitalization Model Award.

163
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,440
Really?

164
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,320
Yes.

165
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,440
I want Xia Village

166
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,000
to win all the awards in the future.

167
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,840
Our secretary really has grand dreams.

168
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,840
I admire you.

169
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:05,100
Actually, it's all thanks to Mr. Yin.

170
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,080
Why bring up Dad Yin?

171
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,540
He encouraged me back then

172
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,920
to speak from the heart.

173
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:13,560
By the way.

174
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,960
I plan to open a processing plant in the village.

175
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,400
We won't be an OEM anymore.

176
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,160
We will recruit talents widely

177
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,080
and do our own research and development.

178
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,610
What do you think, Starman?

179
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,840
It will be very different.
